# day-1
PCA From scratch using iris data set.

This is step by step approach for building pca. It shows How internally sklearnPCA works.
Mainly there are  5  steps:
1. standardize the data
2. eigen decomposition on covariance matrix
3. Select principal components on by using eigen values
4. construct projection matix
5. use this projection matrix to transform features on to new subplace using dot product.
